Christopher Jones (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Jones_(actor) 0 William Frank Jones, better known as Christopher Jones (August 18, 1941 – January 31, 2014), was an American stage, movie, and television actor from Jackson, Tennessee.
